<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>QuickCash Loans Kenya</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>QuickCash Loans Kenya</h1>
  <p>Fast and secure mobile loans directly to M-Pesa</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#about">About</a>
  <a href="#eligibility">Eligibility</a>
  <a href="#terms">Terms</a>
  <a href="#apply">Apply</a>
</nav>

<section id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p>
    QuickCash Loans provides fast and convenient digital loans for Kenyan residents.
    Funds are sent directly to your M-Pesa account after approval.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="eligibility">
  <h2>Eligibility</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Must be 18 years and above</li>
    <li>Must have a valid Kenyan ID</li>
    <li>Must have an active M-Pesa account</li>
    <li>Must provide accurate information</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="terms">
  <h2>Terms & Conditions</h2>

  <p>
    By applying for a loan, you agree to our lending policies and repayment procedures.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>Loans are subject to approval.</li>
    <li>Late repayment may attract penalties.</li>
    <li>False information may lead to rejection.</li>
    <li>User data is protected under Kenya data protection laws.</li>
    <li>Loan limits depend on repayment history.</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section id="apply">
  <h2>Loan Application Form</h2>

  <form onsubmit="submitForm(event)">

    <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" required>

    <input type="text" placeholder="National ID Number" required>

    <input type="tel" placeholder="Phone Number" required>

    <input type="number" placeholder="Loan Amount Needed" required>

    <select required>
      <option value="">Select Repayment Period</option>
      <option>30 Days</option>
      <option>60 Days</option>
      <option>90 Days</option>
    </select>

    <textarea placeholder="Reason for Loan"></textarea>

    <button type="submit">Submit Application</button>

  </form>

  <p id="message"></p>

</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 QuickCash Loans Kenya</p>
</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
